OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1778351320
OL,3,CDriver who killed war veteran after
OL,4,C'pulling wheelies' on motorbike is
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FA motorcyclist who was seen performing
OL,8,F'wheelies' on his bike moments before
OL,9,Fknocking down an elderly war veteran
OL,10,Fin Plymouth has been jailed.
OL,12,FJordan Goody, 26, of Higher Efford
OL,13,FRoad in Plymouth, was riding along
OL,14,FBeacon Park Road on an off-road
OL,15,Fmotorbike when he hit Dilwyn Durham,
OL,16,F80, who was on his way to his local
OL,17,Fsocial club.
OL,19,FThe local man and war veteran later
OL,20,Fdied of his injuries.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
