PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1778351320
OL,3,CDriver who killed war veteran after
OL,4,C'pulling wheelies' on motorbike is
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FGoody was sentenced to six years in
OL,8,Fprison after being found guilty of
OL,9,Fcausing death by dangerous driving.
OL,11,FDuring a trial at Plymouth Crown
OL,12,FCourt, the jury heard that on 5
OL,13,FFebruary 2024, a report came into
OL,14,Fpolice that a KTM motorbike had hit a
OL,15,Fpedestrian and the rider had fled the
OL,16,Fscene.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1778351320
OL,3,CDriver who killed war veteran after
OL,4,C'pulling wheelies' on motorbike is
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FEmergency services attended Beacon
OL,8,FPark Road to find local man Mr Durham
OL,9,Fin a life-threatening condition. The
OL,10,Fcourt heard he died in hospital three
OL,11,Fdays later.
OL,13,FAn investigation was launched and
OL,14,Fofficers identified Jordan Goody as
OL,15,Fthe biker who witnesses reported was
OL,16,F'pulling wheelies' and overtaking cars
OL,17,Fdangerously.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1778351320
OL,3,CDriver who killed war veteran after
OL,4,C'pulling wheelies' on motorbike is
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FIn addition to being jailed, Goody was
OL,8,Fhanded a driving ban of six years,
OL,9,Fwith an extended driving test
OL,10,Frequirement to begin on release from
OL,11,Fprison.
OL,13,FLead investigator Detective Sergeant
OL,14,FSam Pullen, of Devon and Cornwall
OL,15,FPolice's Serious Collisions
OL,16,FInvestigation Unit, said: "While we
OL,17,Fwelcome the sentence Goody has been
OL,18,Fserved, no sentence will ever make up
OL,19,Ffor his mindless actions on that day.
OL,26,@xD@[OU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
