OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1778351320
OL,3,CDriver who killed war veteran after
OL,4,C'pulling wheelies' on motorbike is
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,F"Not only was Goody riding an off-road
OL,8,Fbike, but it also wasn't insured or
OL,9,Flicenced and had no number plate.
OL,11,F"He left the scene of the collision
OL,12,Fwith no regard for human life as Mr
OL,13,FDurham lay dying on the road.
OL,15,F"Mr Durham was a much-loved local man
OL,16,Fwho had also served in the war. He was
OL,17,Fwalking to the local social club that
OL,18,Fday unaware that this would be his
OL,19,Flast outing.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1778351320
OL,3,CDriver who killed war veteran after
OL,4,C'pulling wheelies' on motorbike is
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,F"Goody's decision to drive in an
OL,8,Fincredibly dangerous manner saw one
OL,9,Fman lose his life and left his family
OL,10,Fand friends heartbroken.
OL,12,F"I would like to thank the members of
OL,13,Fthe public who did remain at the
OL,14,Fscene, who I know carry their own pain
OL,15,Ffrom witnessing the aftermath of that
OL,16,Fcollision.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
