OL,3,CDriver who killed war veteran after
OL,4,C'pulling wheelies' on motorbike is
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,F"I would also like to thank the
OL,8,Fcommunity who came forward following
OL,9,Fappeals for information ` your help
OL,10,Fwas invaluable in securing today's
OL,11,Foutcome."
